Jealous lady scalds her boyfriend with hot water In Rivers State. A man identified as Atago Endurance, had a bowl of hot water lavished on him by his jealous girlfriend, last week, in Upatabo, Rivers State. The jealous lady identified as
Uluma poured her boyfriend hot water after she discovered that he is
cheating on her with another girl. Uluma
had wanted to have Atago all to her self alone and never wanted to see
him around another woman according to Onyeka Simeon who broke the news
on social media. Read what he wrote and photos below.   